{"type":null,"faqId":33690,"title":"为什么微信&QQ视频模糊？","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n\"1）微信视频聊天时，默认的相机录像分辨率很低，分辨率只有240*320，所以比较模糊，较低分辨率的图像在大屏更显模糊，这个是由微信&amp;QQ应用自身设置引起的，该设置无法修改，具体的可以咨询微信&amp;QQ客服。使用自带的相机进行拍照录像不会有这样的问题；<br>\n2）在视频聊天时，影像在传输过程中会根据网络状态调节画质，如果网络不佳时容易感觉模糊。<br>\n建议您在网络信号稳定的环境中视频聊天。视频聊天时尽量持稳手机，不要频繁晃动。另外尽量在光线充足的环境中视频聊天。\"<br>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8410","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748697000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":31,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"视频不清晰,视频看不清","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}